WEBVTT

00:09.207 --> 00:10.307
Are you ready, kids?

00:10.309 --> 00:12.275
<i>Aye, aye, Captain!</i>

00:12.277 --> 00:13.577
I can't hear you.

00:13.579 --> 00:16.079
<i>Aye, aye, Captain!</i>

00:16.081 --> 00:18.181
♪ Ohh... ♪

00:18.183 --> 00:20.684
<i>♪ Who lives in a pineapple
under the sea? ♪</i>

00:20.686 --> 00:22.285
<i>SpongeBob SquarePants!</i>

00:22.287 --> 00:24.588
<i>♪ Absorbent and yellow
and porous is he ♪</i>

00:24.590 --> 00:25.822
<i>SpongeBob SquarePants!</i>

00:25.824 --> 00:28.725
<i>♪ If nautical nonsense
be something you wish ♪</i>

00:28.727 --> 00:30.160
<i>SpongeBob SquarePants!</i>

00:30.162 --> 00:32.429
<i>♪ Then drop on the deck
and flop like a fish ♪</i>

00:32.430 --> 00:34.698
<i>- SpongeBob SquarePants!
- Ready?</i>

00:34.700 --> 00:36.800
<i>♪ SpongeBob SquarePants! ♪</i>

00:36.802 --> 00:39.136
<i>♪ SpongeBob SquarePants! ♪</i>

00:39.138 --> 00:41.171
<i>♪ SpongeBob SquarePants! ♪</i>

00:41.173 --> 00:42.506
<i>♪ SpongeBob ♪</i>

00:42.508 --> 00:44.408
<i>♪ SquarePants! ♪</i>

